The second panel includes: Dr. Gracula Quau or Gracula Quan?, Mrs. Mildred Mersereau. The thrid panel includes: Miss Muriel Ferris, John Plauk, Dr. Caroline Ware, Dr. Gracula Quau or Gracula Quan?, Mrs. Mildred Mersereau, and Miss Muriel Ferris.

Workers at local 248 were (from left) Miss Anna Tippelt, 1721 N. 51st st.; Mrs. Eleanor Brockel, 3815 W.
